WEBVTT

00:01:33.410 --> 00:01:34.979
[OVERDO]

00:01:35.180 --> 00:01:37.770
[Episode 3]

00:01:39.740 --> 00:01:42.729
[Three years ago, Nancheng]

00:01:41.950 --> 00:01:42.479
Susu.

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:43.479
I've got news.

00:01:43.759 --> 00:01:45.590
My senior heard about this while performing

00:01:45.590 --> 00:01:46.650
For the Huo family.

00:01:46.759 --> 00:01:49.289
Lan is in a place called Yu Estate in Beicheng.

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:52.039
That is the base camp of the Huo family in Beicheng.

00:01:52.039 --> 00:01:53.120
It's heavily guarded.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:54.560
You must be careful on your journey.

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:56.590
You just need to find out Lan's whereabouts.

00:01:56.590 --> 00:01:57.640
Don't act rashly.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.850
I'll join you shortly after.

00:01:58.850 --> 00:02:00.630
[To Qing]

00:02:30.870 --> 00:02:34.410
[Huo Family's Branch Residence, Yu Estate]

00:02:51.910 --> 00:02:54.280
Thank you for treating my master.

00:02:55.470 --> 00:02:58.670
I heard that Young Master Qingyu has been promoted again.

00:02:59.470 --> 00:03:00.430
My master

00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:02.030
Acquired a few century-old ginseng roots.

00:03:02.030 --> 00:03:04.190
Please bring them to Young Master Qingyu

00:03:04.190 --> 00:03:05.650
To express our gratitude.

00:03:06.030 --> 00:03:07.290
Please keep this gift.

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:09.870
Brother asked me to come here.

00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:12.080
I'm usually in Beicheng.

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:14.000
You should send these gifts

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.710
Directly to my brother.

00:03:19.150 --> 00:03:22.910
[Li Cai, butler of Yu Estate]

00:03:19.710 --> 00:03:21.030
I'll prepare a car for you

00:03:21.030 --> 00:03:22.310
And send you back to the clinic.

00:03:22.310 --> 00:03:23.030
Hold on.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:24.240
Okay.

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:56.120
If you jump from that height,

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:57.360
The probability of fracture

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.630
Is about 70 percent.

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:03.750
If you fall,

00:04:04.310 --> 00:04:05.750
You're most likely to fracture

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:07.810
The fibula and tibia of your two legs,

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:10.400
The ulna of the left arm,

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:13.130
And the finger bones and hamate bones in the palm.

00:04:19.070 --> 00:04:20.399
Mind your own business,

00:04:21.070 --> 00:04:22.470
Or you'll get in trouble.

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:25.630
Fine.

00:04:25.870 --> 00:04:26.630
I'm leaving.

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:29.120
Whether you jump down or stay there

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:29.870
Is up to you.

00:04:30.750 --> 00:04:32.350
You're really a good doctor.

00:04:41.430 --> 00:04:43.120
How did she know I was a doctor?

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.400
Could it be...

00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:56.360
Slowly does it.

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:57.159
Are you okay?

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:01.480
♪ I forgot when it started ♪

00:05:02.420 --> 00:05:04.860
♪ You're always behind me ♪

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:09.840
♪ Silently accompanying me ♪

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:10.690
Is...

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:11.250
Is...

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:13.260
♪ My heart belongs only to you ♪

00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:12.680
Is that you?

00:05:14.280 --> 00:05:16.660
♪ Am I out of my mind? ♪

00:05:19.090 --> 00:05:22.480
♪ It's too late to turn back ♪

00:05:22.950 --> 00:05:23.680
We

00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:28.020
♪ I'll be lonely without you ♪

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.130
Exchanged letters.

00:05:25.390 --> 00:05:26.120
It's me.

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:27.360
Duhuo.

00:05:28.430 --> 00:05:29.490
Do you remember me?

00:05:33.980 --> 00:05:35.820
♪ Our hearts are close ♪

00:05:35.950 --> 00:05:38.540
♪ But our distance is widening ♪

00:05:39.540 --> 00:05:41.540
♪ While silently waiting for your reply ♪

00:05:42.640 --> 00:05:44.580
♪ I've been answering my own questions ♪

00:05:42.750 --> 00:05:43.560
I'm sorry.

00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:45.920
Maybe I mistook you for someone else.

00:05:45.870 --> 00:05:47.490
♪ I constantly confess ♪

00:05:47.580 --> 00:05:50.420
♪ The bitterness in my heart ♪

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:52.070
Do you want to make a bet with me?

00:05:51.500 --> 00:05:54.260
♪ As long as you live happily ♪

00:05:57.070 --> 00:05:57.920
Guess

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.600
♪ I miss you, I miss you ♪

00:05:58.680 --> 00:05:59.900
♪ I miss your hug ♪

00:05:59.159 --> 00:06:00.390
Which bone I broke.

00:05:59.970 --> 00:06:01.450
♪ I miss you, I miss you ♪

00:06:01.530 --> 00:06:03.100
♪ I miss the corners of your lips ♪

00:06:03.180 --> 00:06:04.550
♪ I miss you, I miss you ♪

00:06:04.660 --> 00:06:06.560
♪ I miss every second of you ♪

00:06:06.070 --> 00:06:07.120
If you're right,

00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:10.600
I'll write you a reply.

00:06:09.540 --> 00:06:10.410
♪ I miss you, I miss you ♪

00:06:10.460 --> 00:06:11.720
♪ I miss your hug ♪

00:06:11.820 --> 00:06:13.310
♪ I miss you, I miss you ♪

00:06:13.410 --> 00:06:14.830
♪ I miss the corners of your lips ♪

00:06:14.940 --> 00:06:16.510
♪ I miss you, I miss you ♪

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:17.070
Since the beginning of winter,

00:06:16.580 --> 00:06:18.410
♪ I miss every second of you ♪

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:20.320
Beicheng had experienced many snowfalls.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:22.430
But to me,

00:06:21.440 --> 00:06:23.250
♪ Our hearts are close ♪

00:06:23.350 --> 00:06:26.050
♪ But our distance is widening ♪

00:06:23.750 --> 00:06:25.750
This was the first snow of this year.

00:06:27.010 --> 00:06:28.860
♪ While silently waiting for your reply ♪

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:31.990
♪ I frantically hide the fear in my heart ♪

00:06:33.300 --> 00:06:34.870
♪ I can't confess ♪

00:06:34.970 --> 00:06:37.840
♪ The bitterness in my heart ♪

00:06:38.870 --> 00:06:41.740
♪ As long as you live happily ♪

00:06:46.390 --> 00:06:48.050
♪ I can't help falling ♪

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:51.190
♪ It's a sudden whirlpool ♪

00:06:52.159 --> 00:06:54.409
♪ You don't know I've been here ♪

00:06:56.180 --> 00:06:57.850
♪ Waiting ♪

00:06:56.630 --> 00:06:57.159
Done.

00:06:58.950 --> 00:06:59.550
Thank you.

00:07:05.870 --> 00:07:06.560
You...

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:08.830
How did you recognize me?

00:07:18.120 --> 00:07:19.680
Your mole is very special.

00:07:29.190 --> 00:07:30.680
The chirping grasshoppers

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:32.340
Spring about in lively leaps.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:33.800
I've not seen you in a while.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:35.070
It worries me so.

00:07:43.830 --> 00:07:45.490
Since you wanted to see me too,

00:07:45.510 --> 00:07:46.750
Why didn't you reply?

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:48.270
And why are you

00:07:48.480 --> 00:07:49.510
Here in Beicheng?

00:07:53.830 --> 00:07:54.950
I came to Beicheng

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:56.750
For an important task.

00:07:57.630 --> 00:07:58.960
I had no time to seek you.

00:08:00.870 --> 00:08:01.920
I can help you.

00:08:14.510 --> 00:08:16.160
I want a ribbon.

00:08:19.630 --> 00:08:20.190
Okay.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:29.530
I understood it.

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:31.950
Since she didn't want to elaborate,

00:08:31.950 --> 00:08:33.150
I did not ask further.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.670
Thank you for helping me.

00:08:54.670 --> 00:08:56.000
Let me treat you to dinner.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.000
Just this?

00:08:57.910 --> 00:08:59.510
Of course, we have to eat roasted sweet potatoes in winter.

00:08:59.510 --> 00:09:00.030
Try it.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:01.270
It's very sweet.

00:09:01.270 --> 00:09:01.790
Here.

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:17.000
Your house is quite similar to mine.

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:22.060
My family used to grow many gentian flowers.

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:24.960
It would be great

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:26.960
If you could plant some in your yard.

00:09:30.270 --> 00:09:31.200
When they bloom,

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:33.120
I'll treat you to the great view.

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:36.910
I plant the flowers,

00:09:36.910 --> 00:09:38.440
And you treat me to the view?

00:09:38.790 --> 00:09:40.390
How generous of you.

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.670
Gentian flowers only grow on the plateau.

00:09:43.670 --> 00:09:45.200
My mother spent a lot of effort

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:46.660
Growing them in Nancheng.

00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:49.440
Isn't it enough for me to teach you to grow them?

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:50.840
Fine.

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:52.280
It's very kind of you.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:55.280
In your past letters,

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:57.380
You said you wanted to learn dancing.

00:09:59.240 --> 00:10:00.150
In return,

00:10:00.910 --> 00:10:02.710
You teach me how to grow flowers,

00:10:02.750 --> 00:10:04.810
And I'll teach you to dance the tango.

00:10:15.270 --> 00:10:17.120
After half a year of exchanging letters,

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:18.980
I finally met her in person today.

00:10:19.750 --> 00:10:21.950
Truly, some remain strangers for life,

00:10:22.270 --> 00:10:25.070
While others feel like old friends at first sight.

00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:49.320
[Two months later]

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:47.750
I have an operation tonight.

00:10:47.750 --> 00:10:48.550
When I come back,

00:10:48.550 --> 00:10:50.120
I'll change your dressing again.

00:10:50.120 --> 00:10:51.360
I've recovered.

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:53.450
When the snow stops,

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:55.080
I'll be on my way.

00:10:59.390 --> 00:11:00.240
But we still

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:02.120
Have one dance left to do.

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.840
You're leaving already?

00:11:06.670 --> 00:11:08.870
Thanks for treating my injury.

00:11:14.550 --> 00:11:15.360
Treating you

00:11:16.150 --> 00:11:17.600
Is my duty as a doctor.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:22.090
Whether you go or not

00:11:22.750 --> 00:11:24.030
Is your choice.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:34.520
That was not what I really wanted to say.

00:11:35.510 --> 00:11:36.670
But who was I

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:39.720
To ask her to stay?

00:12:23.750 --> 00:12:24.360
Take care.

00:12:40.960 --> 00:12:41.820
Have you heard?

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.750
The whole of Beicheng is going to have a blackout tonight.

00:12:43.750 --> 00:12:45.870
They said a fight broke out at the Beicheng Power Supply Plant.

00:12:45.870 --> 00:12:48.000
What a time of unrest and uncertainty.

00:12:59.630 --> 00:13:00.960
Why is there a blackout?

00:13:01.150 --> 00:13:02.030
All that's left is to stitch it up.

00:13:02.030 --> 00:13:03.960
But we can't see anything clearly.

00:13:04.790 --> 00:13:05.790
Go and have a look.

00:13:05.910 --> 00:13:06.720
Dr. Murong.

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:07.750
We're here.

00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:10.630
We heard you have surgery today.

00:13:10.630 --> 00:13:12.320
We were afraid the blackout would hinder things.

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:14.180
You often treated our illnesses.

00:13:14.270 --> 00:13:15.800
Now's our time to repay you.

00:13:17.390 --> 00:13:19.630
-We’re here to help you. -How did you know I had surgery?

00:13:19.630 --> 00:13:21.550
Miss Ren knocked on every door

00:13:21.630 --> 00:13:22.320
And asked us to help you.

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:23.440
-Yes. -Yes.

00:13:23.630 --> 00:13:24.670
Miss Ren asked us to come.

00:13:24.670 --> 00:13:25.530
We're all here.

00:13:25.630 --> 00:13:26.360
Thank you.

00:13:26.670 --> 00:13:28.400
I'll finish the surgery first.

00:13:31.150 --> 00:13:31.790
Susu!

00:13:36.270 --> 00:13:36.870
Susu!

00:13:47.030 --> 00:13:47.600
Susu!

00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:52.360
I'm sorry.

00:13:58.870 --> 00:13:59.670
Susu!

00:14:03.910 --> 00:14:04.720
Susu!

00:14:10.550 --> 00:14:11.200
Susu!

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:14.750
Susu!

00:15:09.030 --> 00:15:10.160
The power is back on.

00:15:10.690 --> 00:15:11.790
The lights are back on.

00:15:11.790 --> 00:15:13.050
The lights are back on.

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:13.910
Let's go.

00:15:13.910 --> 00:15:14.710
Let's go home.

00:15:14.870 --> 00:15:16.670
I left food heating on the stove.

00:15:22.270 --> 00:15:23.000
Susu!

00:15:43.240 --> 00:15:44.000
Susu!

00:16:00.360 --> 00:16:01.690
Did the surgery go well?

00:16:01.790 --> 00:16:03.360
The surgery went very well today.

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:04.270
It's all thanks to you.

00:16:04.270 --> 00:16:05.910
The people you sent all brought candles.

00:16:05.910 --> 00:16:07.510
When the candlelight lit up the operating table,

00:16:07.510 --> 00:16:08.200
It felt like

00:16:08.670 --> 00:16:10.000
You were telling me that

00:16:10.030 --> 00:16:11.830
Being a good doctor was worth it.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:18.040
By the way,

00:16:19.360 --> 00:16:19.960
Here.

00:16:23.670 --> 00:16:24.630
Gentian flower?

00:16:25.720 --> 00:16:26.320
Yes.

00:16:27.910 --> 00:16:29.040
I had a friend help me

00:16:29.270 --> 00:16:30.960
Search the highlands for a long time

00:16:30.960 --> 00:16:32.750
Before finally finding this one.

00:16:32.750 --> 00:16:34.840
I wanted to give it to you during the day.

00:16:34.840 --> 00:16:35.840
But this morning,

00:16:35.840 --> 00:16:36.790
I was upset

00:16:37.910 --> 00:16:39.170
That you were leaving.

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:41.630
I thought,

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:43.550
If you really left,

00:16:44.790 --> 00:16:46.080
I wouldn't stop you.

00:16:47.150 --> 00:16:48.200
I'd simply

00:16:49.200 --> 00:16:50.460
Throw this plant away.

00:16:52.480 --> 00:16:53.480
If you don't want it,

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:54.610
I'll take it with me.

00:16:58.870 --> 00:16:59.600
Susu!

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:10.540
We haven't known each other for long.

00:17:11.680 --> 00:17:12.740
A person like me...

00:17:14.750 --> 00:17:16.950
Doesn't deserve anything good anyway.

00:17:17.069 --> 00:17:17.930
I also know that

00:17:18.240 --> 00:17:19.240
There is nothing

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:21.440
We have to keep

00:17:21.589 --> 00:17:22.550
In this world.

00:17:23.790 --> 00:17:24.750
But this time,

00:17:25.829 --> 00:17:27.030
I'd like to try.

00:17:45.030 --> 00:17:45.750
I'm sorry.

00:17:49.070 --> 00:17:50.960
I have something I must do.

00:17:52.830 --> 00:17:53.790
So...

00:17:54.200 --> 00:17:56.200
I know you have things you want to do.

00:17:58.310 --> 00:17:59.840
If you don't want to tell me,

00:18:00.920 --> 00:18:01.750
I won't ask.

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:07.440
But before that,

00:18:08.720 --> 00:18:09.580
Can you spare me

00:18:12.830 --> 00:18:14.750
Even a second of your time?

00:18:17.920 --> 00:18:19.320
Just like me for a second.

00:18:52.750 --> 00:18:54.270
Once the snow stops,

00:18:55.350 --> 00:18:56.480
I should be on my way.

00:18:59.260 --> 00:19:00.770
♪ Running toward you ♪

00:19:01.800 --> 00:19:03.490
♪ From the day I thought ♪

00:19:03.610 --> 00:19:06.430
♪ I succeeded in forgetting you ♪

00:19:08.630 --> 00:19:09.810
♪ Facing the past ♪

00:19:09.950 --> 00:19:12.360
♪ with you inside ♪

00:19:12.440 --> 00:19:14.230
♪ My resolve crumbles ♪

00:19:14.340 --> 00:19:16.470
♪ Immediately ♪

00:19:16.580 --> 00:19:18.980
♪ I'm running ♪

00:19:19.100 --> 00:19:20.980
♪ Running toward you ♪

00:19:22.120 --> 00:19:24.100
♪ No matter how much gossip there is ♪

00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:26.190
♪ I have the courage ♪

00:19:26.290 --> 00:19:31.730
♪ I know you're not far away ♪

00:19:33.560 --> 00:19:35.260
♪ Having loved you deeply ♪

00:19:35.440 --> 00:19:38.570
♪ was the best decision I've made ♪

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:43.830
Murong Qingyi,

00:19:45.070 --> 00:19:47.720
Forgive me for meeting you again in this way.

00:19:50.550 --> 00:19:52.350
But there's something I must do.

00:19:53.110 --> 00:19:54.750
No one can stop me.

00:20:06.550 --> 00:20:07.680
Ren Susu.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:09.030
Stop hiding.

00:20:10.680 --> 00:20:11.880
I miss you so much.

00:20:12.790 --> 00:20:14.440
I think of you day and night.

00:20:15.510 --> 00:20:17.350
I want to skin you

00:20:17.790 --> 00:20:19.240
And break your bones.

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:20.830
Let go of me!

00:20:26.160 --> 00:20:27.960
Your favourite gentian flower.

00:20:29.400 --> 00:20:30.720
Do you still remember it?

00:20:30.720 --> 00:20:32.030
What gentian flower?

00:20:32.350 --> 00:20:33.810
I've never seen it before.

00:20:39.640 --> 00:20:40.720
It's been 3 years.

00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:43.160
You came back from the dead

00:20:43.550 --> 00:20:45.610
Just to set your sights on my brother?

00:20:49.420 --> 00:20:52.140
♪ This spark of wildfire spreading across the plains ♪

00:20:53.160 --> 00:20:55.610
♪ Stirs embers that refuse to fade ♪

00:20:56.750 --> 00:20:59.410
♪ I seize fate by the hand ♪

00:20:59.540 --> 00:21:02.810
♪ Accusing it of refusing to relent ♪

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:06.540
♪ Pain and joy blur before my eyes ♪

00:21:06.400 --> 00:21:07.510
I remember that

00:21:07.540 --> 00:21:10.550
♪ Fate keeps replaying its endless cycle ♪

00:21:10.270 --> 00:21:11.640
Our first kiss

00:21:10.580 --> 00:21:16.120
♪ The love that refused to die ♪

00:21:13.920 --> 00:21:15.380
Tasted exactly like this.

00:21:17.880 --> 00:21:22.580
♪ Has already consumed us both ♪

00:21:20.880 --> 00:21:22.410
About what happened today,

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:24.410
I'll take it as your drunk mistake.

00:21:24.830 --> 00:21:26.830
Do you think you can get away with it?

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:29.070
Ren Susu, listen.

00:21:30.680 --> 00:21:32.880
I'll make you reveal your true identity

00:21:33.110 --> 00:21:34.350
In front of everyone

00:21:34.590 --> 00:21:35.790
And pay the price.

00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:09.510
Young Master Qingyi.

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:10.350
Why are you visiting

00:22:10.350 --> 00:22:12.640
The gentian flower field in the middle of the night?

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:13.700
We'll take our time

00:22:13.830 --> 00:22:15.200
Investigating Miss Ren's matter.

00:22:15.200 --> 00:22:18.060
You mustn't let your emotions get the better of you.

00:22:42.440 --> 00:22:43.440
Ren Susu.

00:22:44.510 --> 00:22:46.550
Were you just using me back then?

00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:48.720
Did you fake your death

00:22:49.160 --> 00:22:50.440
Just to get rid of me?

00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:51.960
Exactly what happened

00:22:52.550 --> 00:22:54.110
3 years ago?

00:23:19.790 --> 00:23:20.440
Susu.

00:23:23.550 --> 00:23:25.000
My family's friend, the Huo family,

00:23:25.000 --> 00:23:26.860
Is holding a banquet in Beicheng.

00:23:26.960 --> 00:23:29.350
My brother asked me to attend it in his stead.

00:23:29.350 --> 00:23:30.240
Come with me.

00:23:49.480 --> 00:23:51.010
Don't like such occasions?

00:23:53.240 --> 00:23:54.480
Is Master Huo

00:23:54.680 --> 00:23:55.790
Their master?

00:23:56.110 --> 00:23:56.640
Yes.

00:24:00.510 --> 00:24:01.750
Does he usually

00:24:01.750 --> 00:24:02.920
Live here?

00:24:03.720 --> 00:24:04.310
Yeah.

00:24:04.960 --> 00:24:05.960
Yu Estate

00:24:05.960 --> 00:24:08.790
Is the base of the Huo Family Chamber of Commerce in Beicheng.

00:24:08.790 --> 00:24:09.790
It can be considered

00:24:09.790 --> 00:24:11.450
Huo Mingxi's private estate.

00:24:13.590 --> 00:24:14.960
Go ahead and do your thing.

00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:16.820
I want to take a walk in the garden.

00:24:17.680 --> 00:24:18.200
Okay.

00:24:18.480 --> 00:24:20.480
I'll pick you up in the garden later.

00:24:20.510 --> 00:24:21.840
We'll go home together.

00:24:45.160 --> 00:24:47.200
Master Huo is dead! Help!

00:24:48.720 --> 00:24:49.880
Huo Mingxi?

00:24:50.680 --> 00:24:51.640
What happened?

00:24:52.830 --> 00:24:53.750
Where is Susu?

00:25:15.350 --> 00:25:17.920
You brought that woman into the Yu Estate, didn't you?

00:25:17.920 --> 00:25:19.550
Now she has disappeared,

00:25:20.350 --> 00:25:22.080
And you were at the crime scene.

00:25:22.510 --> 00:25:23.550
What else do you have to say?

00:25:23.550 --> 00:25:24.440
I didn't kill him.

00:25:24.440 --> 00:25:26.160
Then why did you run away?

00:25:27.480 --> 00:25:28.720
Are you guilty?

00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:30.220
I just want to find her.

00:25:32.680 --> 00:25:33.790
Murong Qingyi.

00:25:34.400 --> 00:25:35.960
I'll give you 3 days.

00:25:36.200 --> 00:25:38.860
You have something to do with that woman anyway.

00:25:39.000 --> 00:25:40.200
If you can't find her,

00:25:40.750 --> 00:25:41.680
You're doomed.

00:25:44.200 --> 00:25:44.920
Susu!

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:46.680
Susu!

00:25:51.240 --> 00:25:51.920
Susu!

00:26:06.510 --> 00:26:06.750
[Closed Today]

00:26:08.910 --> 00:26:10.650
[Pharmacy]

00:26:12.830 --> 00:26:13.780
[You]

00:26:13.680 --> 00:26:15.240
I've asked the Art Academy of Nancheng.

00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:16.230
There has never been

00:26:16.230 --> 00:26:17.680
A student named Ren Susu there.

00:26:17.680 --> 00:26:18.880
We've searched both the east and west districts.

00:26:18.880 --> 00:26:20.160
No trace of Miss Ren.

00:26:20.240 --> 00:26:21.030
Dr. Murong.

00:26:21.160 --> 00:26:22.640
The Huo family has insisted that

00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:24.160
Huo Mingxi's death is related to you.

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.000
You should...

00:26:26.160 --> 00:26:28.020
Do I need you to teach me what to do?

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:44.920
Keep looking.

00:26:46.110 --> 00:26:47.200
Find her

00:26:48.200 --> 00:26:49.510
No matter what it takes.

00:26:49.510 --> 00:26:50.440
-Yes. -Yes.

00:26:55.630 --> 00:26:56.740
[Jiujiekou Street, East District, Beicheng]

00:26:56.760 --> 00:26:58.100
[To: Mr. Duhuo, No. 27 Liuli Hutong]

00:27:03.070 --> 00:27:03.720
Young Master Qingyi.

00:27:03.720 --> 00:27:04.550
Young Master Qingyi.

00:27:04.550 --> 00:27:06.080
We have news about Miss Ren.

00:28:21.880 --> 00:28:22.880
Susu!

00:28:57.440 --> 00:28:58.590
I finally found you.

00:28:58.830 --> 00:28:59.510
Susu.

00:29:02.480 --> 00:29:02.880
Hurry!

00:29:03.110 --> 00:29:03.970
Get out of here.

00:29:04.480 --> 00:29:05.110
Susu.

00:29:07.200 --> 00:29:08.260
On the day you left,

00:29:08.400 --> 00:29:09.600
The flowers bloomed.

00:29:10.270 --> 00:29:11.270
Didn't you tell me

00:29:11.880 --> 00:29:13.540
You would treat me to the view?

00:29:45.680 --> 00:29:47.000
Since we first met,

00:29:47.880 --> 00:29:50.140
I've wanted to sneak into the Huo family.

00:29:50.510 --> 00:29:53.170
Later, I knew you were close with the Huo family,

00:29:53.720 --> 00:29:55.440
So I took advantage of you.

00:30:04.790 --> 00:30:05.960
Don't you get it?

00:30:12.960 --> 00:30:13.790
Why?

00:30:14.750 --> 00:30:16.590
Search every carriage carefully.

00:30:16.590 --> 00:30:18.200
Only these carriages are left.

00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:19.550
She must be in here.

00:30:29.340 --> 00:30:30.390
Get lost!

00:30:31.580 --> 00:30:32.840
Don't you understand?

00:30:36.060 --> 00:30:37.150
I approached you

00:30:37.780 --> 00:30:39.300
Only to use you.

00:30:40.300 --> 00:30:41.150
Did you think

00:30:43.390 --> 00:30:44.910
I really liked you?

00:30:50.950 --> 00:30:52.100
You lied to me.

00:30:58.950 --> 00:30:59.580
Fine.

00:31:02.230 --> 00:31:03.390
I told you,

00:31:04.540 --> 00:31:05.580
I'd have helped you

00:31:05.580 --> 00:31:07.310
With whatever you wanted to do.

00:31:28.060 --> 00:31:29.860
I only have 1 question right now.

00:31:33.260 --> 00:31:34.340
Right now,

00:31:38.230 --> 00:31:39.430
In this second,

00:31:48.150 --> 00:31:49.500
You do like me,

00:31:51.780 --> 00:31:52.500
Right?

00:32:07.950 --> 00:32:08.540
Susu.

00:32:08.740 --> 00:32:09.800
What are you doing?

00:32:11.580 --> 00:32:12.580
Just pretend that

00:32:14.430 --> 00:32:15.780
You've never known me.

00:32:17.230 --> 00:32:18.200
I found her!

00:32:18.490 --> 00:32:19.830
That woman is here!

00:32:47.780 --> 00:32:49.150
Susu!

00:32:50.230 --> 00:32:51.120
Susu!

00:32:51.580 --> 00:32:52.950
Susu!

00:32:55.340 --> 00:32:56.870
Susu!

00:33:24.410 --> 00:33:26.010
♪ The more passionate ♪

00:33:26.130 --> 00:33:28.220
♪ Our past embrace ♪

00:33:31.170 --> 00:33:32.700
♪ The more icy ♪

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:35.030
♪ Our present clash ♪

00:33:37.140 --> 00:33:39.210
♪ If not tangled in love ♪

00:33:40.220 --> 00:33:42.360
♪ We are locked in hate ♪

00:33:43.660 --> 00:33:47.350
♪ There is no escaping it ♪

00:33:51.360 --> 00:33:52.790
♪ Sharper pain, deeper mark ♪

00:33:52.830 --> 00:33:54.880
♪ Deeper care, greater torment ♪

00:33:58.020 --> 00:33:59.110
Ren Susu.

00:33:58.150 --> 00:33:59.200
♪ I won't give up on you ♪

00:33:59.310 --> 00:34:01.590
♪ Don't let go of me ♪

00:34:00.060 --> 00:34:01.150
Three years ago,

00:34:02.470 --> 00:34:04.300
I saw you die with my own eyes.

00:34:04.010 --> 00:34:06.120
♪ Let the ropes of fate ♪

00:34:06.200 --> 00:34:09.000
♪ Bind you and me ♪

00:34:06.500 --> 00:34:08.190
But you came back.

00:34:10.330 --> 00:34:12.530
♪ Even if led to a precipice ♪

00:34:11.260 --> 00:34:12.710
Since you're not dead,

00:34:12.620 --> 00:34:15.270
♪ Together, we fall ♪

00:34:15.570 --> 00:34:17.429
I don't need to keep this anymore.

00:34:17.730 --> 00:34:18.909
♪ Must it take heartache ♪

00:34:18.989 --> 00:34:20.900
♪ To know my heart belongs to you? ♪

00:34:21.800 --> 00:34:23.810
♪ Hearts cold no more ♪

00:34:23.900 --> 00:34:25.380
♪ Is every sweet dream ♪

00:34:25.520 --> 00:34:27.400
♪ Destined to fade away? ♪

00:34:27.610 --> 00:34:31.670
[This footage is a visual effect and not a real shot]

00:34:28.520 --> 00:34:30.070
♪ Don't let it end in smoke ♪

00:34:30.150 --> 00:34:30.860
Young Master,

00:34:30.440 --> 00:34:33.610
♪ Love and hate till the very end ♪

00:34:31.820 --> 00:34:33.480
This field of flowers took you

00:34:33.760 --> 00:34:36.159
♪ Hold nothing back ♪

00:34:33.940 --> 00:34:35.710
So much time, energy,

00:34:35.710 --> 00:34:36.670
And efforts.

00:34:37.520 --> 00:34:40.250
♪ Never back down, hold my ground ♪

00:34:37.710 --> 00:34:39.150
It's such a pity to have it

00:34:39.710 --> 00:34:40.820
All burn away.

00:34:40.400 --> 00:34:42.880
♪ Till I've given my all ♪

00:34:42.190 --> 00:34:43.190
These flowers

00:34:43.040 --> 00:34:44.010
♪ We ♪

00:34:44.900 --> 00:34:46.590
Were meant for the dead, anyway.

00:34:45.370 --> 00:34:47.070
♪ Must be together ♪

00:34:48.230 --> 00:34:50.449
♪ Forevermore ♪

00:34:52.030 --> 00:34:52.830
Young Master.

00:34:53.340 --> 00:34:54.270
My condolences.

00:34:55.070 --> 00:34:55.860
That person

00:34:56.150 --> 00:34:58.010
Must be watching you from heaven.

00:35:04.100 --> 00:35:06.950
♪ Let the tears fall, let the blood spill ♪

00:35:07.080 --> 00:35:09.610
♪ Even through suffering, I'll never let go of your hand ♪

00:35:08.820 --> 00:35:10.190
She won't be in heaven.

00:35:10.560 --> 00:35:13.320
♪ I can't break free, I can't escape ♪

00:35:11.740 --> 00:35:12.780
Someone like her

00:35:13.470 --> 00:35:15.810
♪ This, too, can be called a lifetime together ♪

00:35:13.670 --> 00:35:15.030
Is either in hell,

00:35:16.060 --> 00:35:17.110
♪ We ♪

00:35:16.710 --> 00:35:17.420
Or...

00:35:18.840 --> 00:35:20.380
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

00:35:21.560 --> 00:35:25.510
♪ Forevermore ♪

00:35:22.380 --> 00:35:23.420
But it's fine.

00:35:25.150 --> 00:35:26.380
Since she's back,

00:35:28.630 --> 00:35:29.860
I will ask her

00:35:30.590 --> 00:35:31.700
For an explanation myself.

